{"tid":1394712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂]一起走下去，好嗎？","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:49.000Z","uid":108350,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac5f706111bf034452e7eed00f0d20c5a09de88","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"致同路人：<br />\n<br />\n經歷儼如地獄般的五十多天，我這個廢青其實早已身心累透。<br />\n<br />\n一起回想我們走過的路：<br />\n記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月9日</span>嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62231777_10157729649392448_2931739208756232192_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlqmjY4FlNBHLNjm4wWrey2VBxVMl39uVNg1fE_7LJhWjWJK5llRlxlzc5ESiIw8i4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;oh=252a0971c2982c2513398d195908c870&amp;oe=5DE645B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62231777_10157729649392448_2931739208756232192_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlqmjY4FlNBHLNjm4wWrey2VBxVMl39uVNg1fE_7LJhWjWJK5llRlxlzc5ESiIw8i4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26oh%3D252a0971c2982c2513398d195908c870%26oe%3D5DE645B2&h=c8ec5168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當天<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">103萬</span></span></strong>名香港市民犧牲難得的假期，一起由維園走到立法會，希望用和平的方式令政府回應市民卑微的訴求。記得當天我們流過的汗，走過的路嗎？<br />\n然而政府視而不見，宣佈六月十二日照常二讀。<br />\n<br />\n記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月12日</span>嗎？<br />\n我們<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不畏懼</span></strong>滿身精良裝備的防暴警察，沒有太多保護裝備下希望進入立法會，阻止二讀。你記得義士受過的傷，流過的血嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64387106_10157738893852448_5611218066047238144_n.png?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQkyGPelp4hgEH6545XopTycJm5XPbuTyLy_8bAVeJ76nAzPXuFkGEfPmWlB47kX_Aw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;oh=15e5af6262482d5038d8106f2d4d8ac1&amp;oe=5DA971B3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64387106_10157738893852448_5611218066047238144_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQkyGPelp4hgEH6545XopTycJm5XPbuTyLy_8bAVeJ76nAzPXuFkGEfPmWlB47kX_Aw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26oh%3D15e5af6262482d5038d8106f2d4d8ac1%26oe%3D5DA971B3&h=805217d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1463742_1_20190619110955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1463742_1_20190619110955.jpg&h=8261dc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但，我們卻被政府定性為暴動；對濫用職權、使用警暴的警察卻視若無睹。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n還記得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月15日</span>嗎？<br />\n不幸地，我們之中出現了第一位<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>犧牲者</strong></span></span>：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>梁凌杰</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20190622/LA02/LA02_005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20190622%2FLA02%2FLA02_005.jpg&h=f5fab27b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月16日</span>，我們在做甚麼呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64358589_10157754250812448_2029201721841942528_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQmX-PVXraWwDIUoZisQVQgRyG0K7DfdOzE-i_xR_ER0vvxlT4vNCMWTn_Fp3po3rgc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg7-1.fna&amp;oh=6af90321dce33e27816808d4bda84083&amp;oe=5DDFAC47\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg7-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64358589_10157754250812448_2029201721841942528_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQmX-PVXraWwDIUoZisQVQgRyG0K7DfdOzE-i_xR_ER0vvxlT4vNCMWTn_Fp3po3rgc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg7-1.fna%26oh%3D6af90321dce33e27816808d4bda84083%26oe%3D5DDFAC47&h=b8427bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">200萬+1人</span></span></strong>上街要求政府徹回逃犯條例，同時向烈士致哀。<br />\n曾到太古廣場致意的人，記得當時答應過烈士甚麼嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得你曾說過要替烈士行未完成的路嗎？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>更多的是626到各國領事館遊行、七一強攻立法會、光復屯門、上水、沙田，陳伯絕食苦行，銀髮族遊行，七二一遊行、元朗恐襲，七二七反警黑遊行，728上環苦戰等等等等</strong><br />\n<br />\n在這一刻，你是否仍然在堅持呢？<br />\n<br />\n這些事件我仍然歷歷在目，從未忘記。可見這場運動發展至今，看到的是有人因絕望而放棄，因恐懼而退縮&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你們真的可以放下你的同伴嗎？你對得住提早離隊的烈士嗎？你忍心讓前線義士獨自面對殘害市民生命的警察嗎？</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">更重要的是，你捨得讓香港繼續沉淪嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n時至今日，很多人受傷流血，有很多義士正面臨法律程序，亦有很多市民身心透支，<strong>但我還是咬緊牙關，堅持下去。</strong><br />\n我呼籲正在看這個post的你，不論是文宣、水軍、情感支援等甚麼都好，甚至像我一樣在這發文都可以，請你用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">行動支持</span></span></strong>，因為行動才能讓身邊默默耕耘的人知道：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>他，不是孤身一人！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n我不想要你們的餐劵，食少一兩餐不會死人；<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我更希望日後在香港重見光明之日可一起舉杯慶祝</span></strong>，<br />\n我不想要你們的裝備，單單裝備本身並無任何影響力；<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我更希望你與我一起並肩作戰</span></strong>，<br />\n我不想要你們的同情，因為大家都是受壓迫的人；<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我希望你們可以出多分力，改變現狀</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我和你們一樣，在這場運動中從未看到過曙光。但無論心情有多低落，有多絕望，我也堅守著我的信念：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我們一起走下去，好嗎？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n題外話：我並沒有太多東西可以跟依然保持中立的人分享，因為他們永遠都會堅守道德底線：不容忍任何暴力，影響民生、經濟發展或違反忠君愛國，孝悌的事。我只可以說：在一個完善及公平的制度下，我和你們的看法相同。可惜香港不是。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖片來源: RTHK, 香港蘋果日報, 台灣蘋果日報<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e21a546c20cca5203be5b23416f00866782ac1d5","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"請幫手推到置頂，感激不盡"},{"pid":"f1171565d876c73a77770a0704809154dc1b58ea","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8805d9a593d2503f97fedf0304fc08fa2b8e9749","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0057cfe5e01be58edd31637b54540a37a1821d69","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"386c6bc1e89cf7b6138ca1cecb0538193a34310b","tid":1394712,"uid":45575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13ea277057b2a601d8b8359d5b1e2773a83a97c0","tid":1394712,"uid":273708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"若果大家放棄 之後就未必有得再走嫁啦"},{"pid":"92eef7e637d37dd1134e8e6143155b6a340b6031","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddd5f7e49e26581e3740dfb833a35240909503e4","tid":1394712,"uid":24591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"天佑香港"},{"pid":"13704331829ccf8c3a4649dbbde12509572af067","tid":1394712,"uid":108350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"072e72dd8ce3e4aa4beea868b467aff015ae10c3","tid":1394712,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"永不放棄"},{"pid":"633061cf9e7fa244391534edc8b60ab3e44c5f1e","tid":1394712,"uid":266937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"#香港人，齊上齊落<br />\n#我會參與8月2日集會<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷&nbsp;<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"2f347f7e42d6830f631e98fdcfef072c0291da11","tid":1394712,"uid":266937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"#不放棄，不屈服，香港人，齊上齊落<br />\n#香港人，加油<br />\n#我會參與8月2日集會<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷&nbsp;<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"b1e7460bf26abb3e4faa1e13ed0564e5bad56a